<div  class='flex_column av-2vvxj-21f8e6844b20004a92d134e5df5805f2 av_one_third  avia-builder-el-15  el_before_av_two_third  avia-builder-el-first  first flex_column_div  '     ><div  class='avia-image-container av-2dlzf-863206cf6cd0f0a11b0286cba1d5bf4d av-styling- av-img-linked avia-align-center  avia-builder-el-16  avia-builder-el-no-sibling '   itemprop="image" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" ><div class="avia-image-container-inner"><div class="avia-image-overlay-wrap"><a href="/president/why-higher-education-is-more-important-than-ever/" class='avia_image '  ><picture><source srcset="https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message.webp 1000w,https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-300x240.webp 300w,https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-768x614.webp 768w,https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-705x564.webp 705w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" type="image/webp"><img src="https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message.jpg" height="800" width="1000" srcset="https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message.jpg 1000w, https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-300x240.jpg 300w, https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-768x614.jpg 768w, https://sou.edu/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/SOU-President-Rick-Bailey-Importance-of-Higher-Ed-Message-705x564.jpg 705w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" class="wp-image-21016 avia-img-lazy-loading-not-21016 avia_image  sp-no-webp" alt="SOU President Rick Bailey Importance of Higher Ed Message" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" itemprop="thumbnailUrl"  > </picture></a></div></div></div></div><div  class='flex_column av-1mfif-0c00f2f0a377074d6144d8c7b11e5cdf av_two_third  avia-builder-el-17  el_after_av_one_third  avia-builder-el-last  flex_column_div  '     ><div  class='av-special-heading av-s78n-78938d04a701ee6af099786c29a18815 av-special-heading-h2 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote  avia-builder-el-18  el_before_av_textblock  avia-builder-el-first  amazing-head av-thin-font av-inherit-size'><h2 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop="headline"  ><strong>Why Higher Education is More Important than Ever</strong></h2><div class="special-heading-border"><div class="special-heading-inner-border"></div></div></div>
<section  class='av_textblock_section av-m48vk726-48f78bfb2870aac5ee2323233b379ce0 '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock right-pillow force-mossy-link av_inherit_color'  itemprop="text" ><p>President Bailey admits he’s biased toward higher education – and the value of a liberal arts education. But objectively, there are many advantages that can’t be overlooked: nearly a million extra dollars in lifetime earnings; higher rates of personal satisfaction and professional advancement; a better appreciation of everything around you that comes with “learning how to learn;” the marketplace of ideas found on university campuses; the intellectual flexibility that comes from a broad-based education; and the “soft skills” in communication, creativity, problem-solving and leadership that employers prize. <a href="/president/why-higher-education-is-more-important-than-ever/">Read More Here</a></p>
</div></section></div>

</div></div></div><!-- close content main div --></div></div><div id='av_section_4'  class='avia-section av-njm07-ecedd72da9d9ad94b4d944f3e9dddf7c alternate_color avia-section-default avia-no-border-styling  avia-builder-el-20  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_section  get-faded-back avia-bg-style-scroll container_wrap fullsize'  ><div class='container av-section-cont-open' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-51'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
