<div  class='av-special-heading av-136ehz-b8c5f298dea0f8da507e3195fc50fba0 av-special-heading-h2 custom-color-heading blockquote modern-quote modern-centered  avia-builder-el-41  el_before_av_textblock  avia-builder-el-first  amazing-head av-thin-font av-inherit-size'><h2 class='av-special-heading-tag '  itemprop="headline"  ><strong>Southern Oregon University Welcomes Transfer Students!</strong></h2><div class="special-heading-border"><div class="special-heading-inner-border"></div></div></div>
<section  class='av_textblock_section av-12ctj3-a48122bb12e4bb5e9c8c09b86b96851f '   itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock small-pillow av_inherit_color'  itemprop="text" ><p>At SOU, we’re excited to embrace transfer students into our vibrant academic community! Maximize your previous college experience with our generous acceptance of transfer credits. Many of our programs are designed specifically for you, allowing you to transfer with at least Junior status while having all your lower division general education requirements completed.</p>
<p>Ready to take the next step? Discover how you can qualify and start your journey toward an enriching educational experience at SOU! See how to qualify. Join us and unlock your potential at Southern Oregon University!</p>
</div></section>
<div  class='avia-button-wrap av-11r5z7-d6bf87734fdac5315d6c623028fb518c-wrap avia-button-center  avia-builder-el-43  el_after_av_textblock  avia-builder-el-last '><a href='/admissions/apply/transfer/'  class='avia-button av-11r5z7-d6bf87734fdac5315d6c623028fb518c av-link-btn avia-icon_select-no avia-size-x-large avia-position-center avia-color-light'   aria-label="SEE HOW TO QUALIFY"><span class='avia_iconbox_title' >SEE HOW TO QUALIFY</span></a></div>
</p>
